      "lead_silence_s": 0.5,
      "narration_text": "Let's recap with Claude. The metaprompt takes a plain two-sentence task description and outputs a full production prompt template. It applies Anthropic's prompting best practices automatically, delegating the first draft rather than skipping the work. The template has six components: role, context, input format, instructions, output format, and edge cases. It cannot know your schema or production failures, so generate, test on real inputs, and iterate before shipping.",
