      "narration_text": "I like that the metaprompt turns two plain sentences into a six-component template but cannot know my production edge cases. I want to run the full loop on something real. Can you (1) take a two-sentence task description I give you and generate the six-component template, role through edge cases, (2) point out specifically which components it had to guess because my data schema was unknown, and (3) hand me three real inputs to test the draft on so I can see where it fails before I promote it?",
