      "beat_id": "B01",
      "scene": "B01_MetapromptIO",
      "narration_text": "The metaprompt has one input and one output. Input: a plain-language task description — two sentences, no structure required. Output: a complete prompt template with all the components a production prompt needs. The metaprompt applies Anthropic's own prompting best practices automatically. You are not skipping the work of prompt engineering — you are delegating the first draft to a system that has read the manual.",
